item.dc:creator: @sk1ttlezrule43v sk1ttlezrule43v
item.description:
@sk1ttlezrule43v wrote:

It’s not that hard. Go down in the files and look for something like ‘Run.Bat’. Don’t get confused with ‘Build’ or ‘Compile’. It also might say ‘Inisualize’. Anything ranging from that. Any other questions or problems. You can pm me.
